DJ AND music producer Mo Flava is officially off the market. The talented musician, whose real name is Moeti Tsiki, recently took to Facebook and announced that he has married his long-term girlfriend Mbali Cele. In a brief post, Mo Flava, who hosts Metro FM’s breakfast show The Morning Flava, said introduced Mzansi to Mr and Mrs Tsiki. “Meet Mr and Mrs Tsiki. Done and dusted. My mission is to make Mbali happy for the rest of her life.” “It will be accomplished. Celebrations loading! She deserves only the best,” he said. The talented DJ is the second celebrity who recently got married and was mum about it. In August, Mafikizolo group member Theo Kgosinkwe married his girlfriend Vourne and since then they have announced that they are expecting their first child together.